title.rendered: SNCF Réseau tests the CyFENCE product

content.rendered:
After three months of evaluation of the CyFENCE product on its robustness and functions, SNCF Réseau confirms a positive result!

We are pleased to continue our collaboration by providing them our expertise in industrial cyber security.

Read the press release.
